38
00:02:11,150 --> 00:02:12,350
Our officials are women.

39
00:02:12,350 --> 00:02:13,920
Our City Owner is a woman.

40
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,920
All men are boors

41
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:17,670
