Move away.

56
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:47,360
Get lost. You. All of you get lost.

57
00:02:49,830 --> 00:02:51,550
Get her. Move away.

58
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:11,150
Get out of the way.

59
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,790
