in the presence of Han Shuo.

515
00:26:26,070 --> 00:26:28,070
Of course I won't.

516
00:26:28,710 --> 00:26:29,520
In case

517
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:31,280
I really offend Han Shuo,

518
00:26:32,310 --> 00:26:34,070
